ERRORS/MISCELLANEOUS
--------------------
The -fnovisi patch completely disables the -fvisibility=hidden
support since gcc using the native linker ignores it anyway.
The -dmedia patch adds an extra compatibility define
Without the -ifdef patch the build will fail complaining about
#if with empty condition.
